{"tid":2364583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"避答高官、家人是否英藉","createTime":"2021-01-13T06:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T06:05:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e821eb9a01210cfbc36e04521555247bfa2f774f","tid":2364583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/FIHJZTL4PRH4BOPVEBLZBP3B4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FFIHJZTL4PRH4BOPVEBLZBP3B4M%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=2e2ea54e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FFIHJZTL4PRH4BOPVEBLZBP3B4M%2F&h=5efbe570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/FIHJZTL4PRH4BOPVEBLZBP3B4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n避答高官、家人是否英藉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qmPfUx-gd9BN7eYqRjbWgHmUpxg=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UR37HFIC3NEL3BVK6PYJMSQRSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqmPfUx-gd9BN7eYqRjbWgHmUpxg%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUR37HFIC3NEL3BVK6PYJMSQRSM.jpg&h=d3ff7b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林鄭避答其家人是否持有英籍。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥表示，回歸前中英政府對BNO問題曾有共識，若有一方單方面處理「有偏頗」，另一方採取行動理所當然，但未正面回應現時政府對公務員是否持BNO或外國國籍的問題，就連其家人是否仍有英國國籍也沒有再交代。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「港配合京反制BNO」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常秘首長多擁居英權<br />\n<br />\n身兼行會成員的新民黨葉劉淑儀早前提出嚴格執行《中國國籍法》，使持有外國國籍的港人自動失去特區護照權利、香港居留權和投票權後，網媒「眾新聞」昨引述資深政務官的說法指，不少現為常任秘書長或部門首長的高級政務官，都是80至90年代加入政府，相信他們透過港英年代計劃獲得居英權，惟向所有常秘和部門首長查詢後，當局僅表示除《基本法》第101條規定的例外情況，《基本法》並無對公務員的國籍或所持有的護照訂明要求。<br />\n<br />\n1980年加入政府的林鄭月娥，。。。。。。。。"}]}